<plot>In a dark, fairytale world; a mother has impending dreams about a demon that lurks in the forest outside. On a hunting trip she takes her two daughters with her as usual - but on this day one daughter is lured into the demon's layer using it's puppet but mother manages to pull her daughter free - mother hits her straying daughter and they go home. Later that night the demon penetrates the family home and possesses mother creating a monster out of her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?013595</url></doc>
